headline: Tesla, Netflix set to report earnings as US-China trade fight turns 'unsustainable': What to watch this week
summary: As investors enters shutdown week three, a US-China trade war, credit gesticulation, and an incoming oil glut are weighing on the market.

headline: Valero Energy (VLO): Evaluating Valuation After Strong Multi-Year Shareholder Returns and Industry Shifts
summary: Valero Energy (VLO) shares have been relatively steady lately, even as energy markets show mixed signals. Investors are watching how the company’s financial track record translates in a market shaped by evolving supply and demand dynamics. See our latest analysis for Valero Energy.
